Information We Collect
Information you give us
You choose to give us certain information when using our services. This includes:
When you create an account, you provide us with at least one of the following: your phone number, email address, Facebook social login, Apple ID, or Google Gmail address, as well as some basic details necessary for the service to work, such as chosen name and date of birth.
When you complete your profile, you can share with us additional information, such as details on your bio and content such as photos. To add certain content, like pictures, you may allow us to access your camera or photo album.
When you subscribe to a paid service or make a purchase directly from us, you provide us or our payment service provider with financial information.
If you contact our customer care team, we collect the information you give us during the interaction.
We also process your chats with other members as well as the content you publish, as necessary for the operation of the services.
